            <div><span class="aihub-eyebrow">Related workflows</span><h2>Build a faster review loop</h2></div>
            <p>Start with OCR for scanned PDFs, summarize the result, ask follow-up questions, then export or share only the final document. AI outputs are not legal advice.</p>
            <div class="aihub-workflow-links">
                <a href="/pdf-ocr">OCR scanned PDFs</a>
                <a href="/converter">Browse converters</a>
                <a href="/business-pdf-tools">Business workflows</a>
