            <div class="aihub-section-header">
                <span class="aihub-eyebrow">Questions</span>
                <h2 id="aihub-faq-title">AI PDF tools FAQ</h2>
            </div>
            <div class="aihub-faq-grid">
                <article><h3>What are AI PDF tools?</h3><p>They are workflows that use AI to summarize, translate, compare, rewrite, review, or extract information from PDF documents.</p></article>
                <article><h3>Do I need an account?</h3><p>AI tools require sign-in so usage limits and document workflows can be handled securely.</p></article>
                <article><h3>Are AI tools free?</h3><p>Signed-in users can start with free AI uses when available. Higher-volume workflows require Pro.</p></article>
                <article><h3>Are files stored?</h3><p>Files are processed securely and deleted within the normal retention window. Avoid uploading documents you are not authorized to process.</p></article>
                <article><h3>Can AI review legal documents?</h3><p>AI-assisted contract analysis may help identify risks and key terms, but AI outputs are not legal advice.</p></article>
                <article><h3>Do AI tools work on scanned PDFs?</h3><p>Scanned PDFs usually need OCR first so recognized text is available to AI workflows.</p></article>
            </div>
        </section>
